    "The SAM model significantly outperforms state-of-the-art methods, demonstrating superior semantic alignment and coherence in multi-modal instructions.Figure 2:2Figure 2: Demonstration of our proposed 2-step sample synthesis pipeline.",
    "We begin by selecting images featuring characters in different poses (A), along with 2 another distinct characters (B, C).",
    "The selected images are segmented to isolate each character, after which they are merged into mask images.",
    "Inpainting technology is then utilized to fill in the background areas of these mask images to obtain the final images, using descriptions generated by ChatGPT.",
    "Text annotations are generated by InstructBLIP and further refined with ChatGPT."
